S"You are now treading water underneath the bridge that crosses the lagoon.  There are many reeds and slimy plants growing between you and the eastern shore of the lagoon,  so you wouldn't be able to swim that way."
sg22
S"You may swim North towards a small coral reef, South to the water's edge, or if you were better at holding your breathe under water, you might consider swimming down below the water's surface."
