S'You are now standing on a ledge that juts out of the interior wall of a volcano. The heat here is intense beyond explanation or comprehension, and begin to feel a little dizzy. Adding curiousity to this exotic locale, a large grey metal ring hangs from the ceiling at the end of the hand-carved volcanic cave.'
sg22
S'You have no interest in jumping Down into the lava below you, so you may only return South, to the cool ocean air at the other end of the volcanic cave.'
