S"You now stand on the top of a volcano, peering down at the lava flowing deep within it. The heat emanating from within the bowels of the earth blast your face with a ferousity that causes you to snap your head back. Before averting you eyes, you happen to glance a certain dark splotch off to the side of the volcano's interior."
sg22
S'You can go Down the north side of the volcano, or SouthEast down a path that wraps around to the southern face.'
