sg4
S'You are in the entrance to a volcanic cave.'
sg5
S'Original Text went as follows: You are resting inside a naturally-formed dugout, probably shaped and molded by the lava the last time the volcano erupted. The dugout resemble a very small cave, about seven feet deep into the volcano, six feet high, and six feet wide. Its deep enough to block out the sun, but wide enough to let in the refreshing sea breeze.'
sg6
