S"There is a small uncovered well here, in the middle of the green pasture. You can hear water flowing at the bottom, and the smell of saltwater hangs in the air. Wide cliffs overhang the ocean below to the north, while to the south a path gently twists it's way through a pasture and up a hill. A small wooden structure is built into the well, with a crank system for raising an lowering a bucket into the water below."
sg22
S'From the well, you can travel North towards the northern cliffs of the island, or south along the faint path that works its way uphill across the pasture.'
