S'You are standing on a cobblestone path that leads in between a tall greyish-white wall and the immense ruins of a once-great manor. The odor of decaying wood drifts radiates through the air from the remains of the old building to the east. You have absolutely no desire to crawl around that dirty heap of debris. The cobblestone path continues south, towards the partial remains of a much smaller building, nestled in between the wall and a few bushes, overgrown with weeds.'
sg22
