S'You are crawling along an underground passageway that declines to the north. The light cast by the fungi growing in the soil appears to grow stronger the further down into the earth you continue. Ahead to the north you just make out that this particular tunnel appears to terminate as it enters a small subterraignian chamber. To the south, the tunnel rises to a point where it forks into three directions.'
sg22
S'You can go North to the room at the end of the tunnel, or South to where the tunnel forks.'
